    <article>
        <h3>The museum</h3>
        <p>
            The first museum in the Netherlands that focuses entirely on media art.
            Explore large-scale digital art installations that broaden your perspective and sharpen the senses. 
            The art of tomorrow, today.
        </p>
        
        <img class="foto1" src="img/nxt 1.jpg" alt="een man tussen lichtstralen">
        <img class="foto2" src="img/nxt 2.jpg" alt="een lichtshow">
        <img class="foto3" src="img/nxt 3.jpg" alt="">

        <p class="geschidenis">
            Nxt Museum is the first museum in the Netherlands that focuses entirely on media art. 
            We exhibit artworks that utilize modern technologies of the present and the future. 
            Because art reflects the spirit of the times, 
            we believe that the most innovative art provides us with the opportunity to reflect on the impact of technological developments. 
            A moment of contemplation in a reality that is constantly evolving at an accelerated pace.
        </p>
            Address
            Nxt Museum
            Asterweg 22
            1031HP Amsterdam

            Opening Hours
            Sun-Tue: 10:30 am - 8:30 pm
            Wed: 11:00 am - 9:30 pm
            Thu-Sat: 10:30 am - 10:30 pm
        <p>

        </p>
